OL,3,CPost Office campaigner Sir Alan Bates
OL,4,Cknighted at Windsor Castle
OL,6,FSir Alan Bates, the leading campaigner
OL,7,Ffor subpostmasters in the Post Office
OL,8,FHorizon IT scandal, has received his
OL,9,Fknighthood at Windsor Castle.
OL,11,FThe 70-year-old, from Wales, is one of
OL,12,Fmore than 550 claimants who have
OL,13,Fbrought legal action against the
OL,14,Fcompany, with a public inquiry into
OL,15,Fwhat happened in its final stages.
OL,17,FHe was recognised in the King's
OL,18,FBirthday Honours in June for his
OL,19,Fservices to justice, having founded
OL,20,Fthe Justice for Subpostmasters
OL,21,FAlliance.
