OL,3,CPost Office campaigner Sir Alan Bates
OL,4,Cknighted at Windsor Castle
OL,6,FMore than 700 subpostmasters were
OL,7,Fprosecuted by the Post Office and
OL,8,Fgiven criminal convictions between
OL,9,F1999 and 2015, as Fujitsu's faulty
OL,10,FHorizon IT system made it appear as
OL,11,Fthough money was missing at their
OL,12,Fbranches.
OL,14,FSpeaking after receiving a knighthood
OL,15,Ffor his services to justice at Windsor
OL,16,FCastle on Wednesday, Sir Alan said the
OL,17,FLabour Government has not contacted
OL,18,Fsubpostmasters and has left them "at a
OL,19,Fstandstill" over the scandal.
