OL,3,CPost Office campaigner Sir Alan Bates
OL,4,Cknighted at Windsor Castle
OL,6,F"They (the Government) haven't been in
OL,7,Fcontact about what they're proposing
OL,8,Fto do yet.
OL,10,F"We think we've come to a standstill
OL,11,Fwith most of the schemes in that they
OL,12,Fdon't seem to be working, they seem to
OL,13,Fbe failing now."
OL,15,FSir Alan, of Llandudno, said the
OL,16,Foriginal claimants are now calling on
OL,17,Fthe Government to set a deadline for
OL,18,Fthe initial GLO compensation scheme.
