OL,3,CPost Office campaigner Sir Alan Bates
OL,4,Cknighted at Windsor Castle
OL,6,FHe said: "We're wanting a completion
OL,7,Fdate guaranteed by the Government for
OL,8,Fthe end of March next year, and it's
OL,9,Fquite achievable, according to legal
OL,10,Fdiscussions I've had.
OL,12,F"I think we've got to get rid of the
OL,13,Fbureaucracy that's holding the whole
OL,14,Fthing up and driving it into the
OL,15,Fground, and it's proving such a
OL,16,Fheadache for so many of the victims
OL,17,Fwho are still suffering after so many
OL,18,Fyears."
OL,20,FSir Alan said: "The Post Office is as
OL,21,Fbad as ever.
