OL,3,CPost Office campaigner Sir Alan Bates
OL,4,Cknighted at Windsor Castle
OL,6,F"The financial redress schemes are
OL,7,Fjust not working to the extent that
OL,8,Fthey should, and it's just a mess.
OL,10,F"It needs to be taken out of
OL,11,FGovernment's hands, and it needs to be
OL,12,Fput into an organisation that can
OL,13,Fresolve things very, very quickly
OL,14,Fbecause it's gone on too long, and
OL,15,Fpeople are still suffering."
