OL,3,CPost Office campaigner Sir Alan Bates
OL,4,Cknighted at Windsor Castle
OL,6,FThe campaigner said he has "great
OL,7,Fhopes" for the ongoing Metropolitan
OL,8,FPolice investigation into potential
OL,9,Findividuals and corporate entities
OL,10,Finvolved in the scandal, but feels it
OL,11,Fwill take "at least a couple of years"
OL,12,Ffor any charges to be brought.
OL,14,FSir Alan was knighted by the Princess
OL,15,FRoyal on Wednesday for his services to
OL,16,Fjustice, having been recognised in the
OL,17,FKing's Birthday Honours in June.
