OL,6,FSir Alan was portrayed by actor Toby
OL,7,FJones in the ITV drama Mr Bates Vs The
OL,8,FPost Office, with the four-part mini-
OL,9,Fseries helping to renew attention on
OL,10,Fthe scandal.
